{"tid":1907701,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"咁撚多廢話做乜？只要係公務員就唔係手足！","createTime":"2020-03-02T19:13:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T06:09:29.000Z","uid":126329,"like":15,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"feedeab4e57fe4c136a61a492c2e2e07d92b2155","tid":1907701,"uid":126329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T19:13:40.000Z","msg":"你地要將個層面提升到 只要公務員唔罷工 聽指示做野既就係走狗 唔係同路人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>而邏輯上公務員罷工 &amp; 唔聽指示做野就會被炒(呢樣野無討論空間 有晒指引守則 炒你跟足程序）<br />\n結論就係公務員根本無可能會係手足 手足認證就係比人炒</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n原理同係連燈討論戰線 只要無自拍抗爭照片（打緊仗帶兩部機出去 一部開著連燈acc 另一部自拍否則都唔可以證明係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)就無人權一撚樣<br />\n全部都要曝晒光 對家都有證據做到你既先可以叫有credit<br />\n<br />\n我既立場好簡單<span style=\"color: orange;\">如果你地純粹討論公務員既薪金與工作表現唔成正比完全無問題</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但如果你地將呢樣野拉去公務員不可做同路人呢件事上面<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咁我屌你地班分化撚老母都算合理掛？</span><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"277f77809310f4b200f3c764669a979191992660","tid":1907701,"uid":126329,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T19:18:02.000Z","msg":"點 分化狗仲有乜理論 想割公務員？"},{"pid":"cacb717f788f2b46a0e841287896cd94960feb88","tid":1907701,"uid":126329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T19:18:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e9db34870ddf9311dd87dd083140aa916442bce","tid":1907701,"uid":237581,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"277f77809310f4b200f3c764669a979191992660","tid":1907701,"uid":126329,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T19:18:02.000Z","msg":"點 分化狗仲有乜理論 想割公務員？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":